* https://github.com/gabrielmontagne/tw-fountain

* Render [[Fountain|https://fountain.io/]] screenplays in [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com/]].

* Wraps [[Fountain-js|https://github.com/jonnygreenwald/fountain-js]], with [[JsonML|https://github.com/mckamey/jsonml]] and a pinch of [[CMU's typewriter font|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_Modern]].

* Based on the [[Bimlas's|https://github.com/bimlas]] [[Asciidoc|https://github.com/bimlas/tw5-asciidoctor]] plugin.

* To install on your own TiddlyWiki, simply drag this link to it, [[$:/plugins/tm/tw-fountain]].
